\item \emph{hyperbolic}, if $\gg$ is a nontrivial translation (equivalently, if $\mov(\gg) = \{\lambda\}$ for $\lambda \neq 0$, or if $\fixaff(\gg) = \varnothing$ and $\fixlin(\gg) = V$); and
