Let $X,Y \subseteq G_{k}$ be fixed.
Suppose that $H \in \But(n,k)$ such that every entry of $H$ is contained in $X$,
and that $M \in \But(m,\ell)$ such that every eigenvalue of $\sqrt{m}^{-1}M$ is contained in $Y$.

